y</cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2013/03/slow-cooker-jerk-chicken/#comment-80508\">05.21.13 at 6:09 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>This was a big hit with grandchildren to grandad.   The ease of the crockpot makes this a recipe I would  make often. I  was  tapering off on the amount of cooking I needed to do after 36  years of marriage, then two family members, one a child  moved in with us. Back to seven days of cooking, dishes and  grocery shopping, so the ease and tastiness of this recipe puts it at the top of my  list!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/03/slow-cooker-jerk-chicken/?replytocom=80508#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-80508\", \"80508\", \"respond\", \"13074\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-80964\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e5bf7a814eb034d8da9c9896f7b11533?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\">Sean</cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2013/03/slow-cooker-jerk-chicken/#comment-80964\">06.02.13 at 11:02 am</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>Could I add vegetables to this recipe and make my whole meal in the slow cooker</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2013/03/slow-cooker-jerk-chicken/?replytocom=8