roilers are different. Broilers can quickly burn food because of their high heat and close proximity of the heat source."], "images": [{"url": "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-Y9CdSkLEkY8/UTPJro-ky7I/AAAAAAAAJ3A/wYuwq_scSXc/s640/Jerk+Chicken+platter.jpg", "path": "full/97ff1992b261da97000cb793b9b57767d298aecb.jpg", "checksum": "c7e3586fcf4d3a8ddeb1a3dc638b2654"}], "link": "http://www.budgetbytes.com/2013/03/slow-cooker-jerk-chicken/", "recipe_cook_time": ["PT4H10M"], "recipe_yield": ["4-6"]}